title: 3br/2 ba Concord Home on Walnut Creek Border
posting_body: Great house in a nice family orientated Concord Neighborhood on the Walnut Creek border!
Excellent commute location minutes to Pleasant Hill Bart, 680 and the Country Wood shopping center.
1,400 square foot home with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a 2 car garage on a quiet street.
Nice size landscaped backyard with patio.
Gardener, garbage, refrigerator, washer and dryer included with rent!
